<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 16:08:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>埃尔多安和土耳其在加沙地区危机中被边缘化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/erdogan-and-turkey-have-been-sidelined-in-the-gaza-based-regional-crisis/00000190-2b6f-dafe-a3d6-3f6f30ee0000</link><description>在土耳其总统抨击以色列和拜登政府的同时，他也试图保护自己国家的利益，例如与以色列盟友阿塞拜疆的经济关系。不管怎样，“第二天”的会谈中没有他的座位</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/erdogan-and-turkey-have-been-sidelined-in-the-gaza-based-regional-crisis/00000190-2b6f-dafe-a3d6-3f6f30ee0000</guid></item><item><title>“黎巴嫩，应许之地的一部分”：以色列救世主右翼瞄准新的定居点领土</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-part-of-the-promised-land-israels-messianic-right-wing-targets-new-territory/00000190-2b9d-d340-a1f8-2b9d18220000</link><description>在你对周一举行小型在线会议、着眼于夺回“上帝应许之地”的宗教弥赛亚主义者不屑一顾之前，请记住，他们的约旦河西岸定居点计划在 50 年前似乎同样古怪</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-part-of-the-promised-land-israels-messianic-right-wing-targets-new-territory/00000190-2b9d-d340-a1f8-2b9d18220000</guid></item><item><title>报告：新证据显示以色列国防军事先详细了解哈马斯袭击以色列的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/report-new-evidence-reveals-idf-had-detailed-prior-knowledge-of-hamas-plan-to-raid-israel/00000190-2afb-d2de-af9e-6ffbdf700000</link><description>一份前所未见的以色列国防军文件揭示了哈马斯入侵以色列行动计划的令人震惊的新细节；报告概述哈马斯下令劫持 200 至 250 名以色列人作为人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/report-new-evidence-reveals-idf-had-detailed-prior-knowledge-of-hamas-plan-to-raid-israel/00000190-2afb-d2de-af9e-6ffbdf700000</guid></item><item><title>沙斯威胁退出联盟，利库德集团因反对有争议的法案而将议员从议会委员会中除名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mks-mayors-spar-over-contentious-bill-giving-govt-control-of-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-2b82-d39e-a999-7fce7a3d0000</link><description>以色列市长们认为，在以色列努力应对加沙战争以及与真主党日益紧张的情况下，联盟成员不应该浪费时间争论赋予政府任命城市拉比权力的立法</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:39:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mks-mayors-spar-over-contentious-bill-giving-govt-control-of-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-2b82-d39e-a999-7fce7a3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察加大对示威者的镇压，以色列议员称反政府抗议者是“哈马斯的手臂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mk-calls-anti-govt-protesters-arm-of-hamas-as-police-crackdown-on-protests-intensifies/00000190-2ae2-d95e-a3ff-eef60c280000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡总理耶路撒冷官邸外举行的示威活动中，三名反政府抗议者受伤，九人被捕。利库德集团议员尼西姆·瓦图里后来澄清了他的声明，称他对自己的言论感到“震惊”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mk-calls-anti-govt-protesters-arm-of-hamas-as-police-crackdown-on-protests-intensifies/00000190-2ae2-d95e-a3ff-eef60c280000</guid></item><item><title>现在是参观以色列戈兰高地的最佳时机（忽略真主党的火箭弹）</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-is-throwing-rockets-but-golan-heights-locals-think-you-should-still-vacate-here/00000190-217b-d4b4-a7d6-e9fb431e0000</link><description>以旅游业为生的戈兰高地居民恳求以色列人回来参观，并承诺这里一如既往的安全</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-is-throwing-rockets-but-golan-heights-locals-think-you-should-still-vacate-here/00000190-217b-d4b4-a7d6-e9fb431e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵命令巴勒斯坦未成年人处理他藏在祖父家中的爆炸物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-order-palestinian-minor-to-handle-explosives-he-had-hidden/00000190-2a38-d5f5-a5d6-ebfa0b1e0000</link><description>本月早些时候，这名巴勒斯坦少年在带领以色列军队制造炸弹后在盖勒吉利耶被捕。以色列国防军上传的视频显示，这名青少年正在清除屋外的爆炸物，以色列国防军消息人士称这没有问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-order-palestinian-minor-to-handle-explosives-he-had-hidden/00000190-2a38-d5f5-a5d6-ebfa0b1e0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：内塔尼亚胡问警方为什么“没有一个激进犹太人”因杀害巴勒斯坦人而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-police-why-not-single-radical-jew-arrested-in-killing-of-palestinians/00000190-29f6-d340-a1f8-29f613450000</link><description>在一份披露的录音中，以色列安全官员在会议期间发生争吵，而内塔尼亚胡在美国的压力下敦促采取行动打击定居者的暴力行为</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-police-why-not-single-radical-jew-arrested-in-killing-of-palestinians/00000190-29f6-d340-a1f8-29f613450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院听取了反对将警察隶属于极右翼部长本-格维尔的法律的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-hears-petitions-against-law-subordinating-police-to-far-right-minister/00000190-2a8c-d2de-af9e-6feef23a0000</link><description>国家检方认为，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的法律创造了“一个不平衡的政府体系，使警察部队的使用政治化”。请愿者称这是违宪的</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 09:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-hears-petitions-against-law-subordinating-police-to-far-right-minister/00000190-2a8c-d2de-af9e-6feef23a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙逮捕了一名高级医生。六天后，他死于辛贝特审讯所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-arrested-a-senior-doctor-in-gaza-six-days-later-he-died-in-a-shin-bet-facility/00000190-27eb-d14b-a999-27eb9aea0000</link><description>53 岁的伊亚德·兰蒂西 (Iyad Rantisi) 医生在加沙北部的拜特拉希亚 (Beit Lahiya) 经营一家妇女医院。 《辛贝特》称，他因涉嫌扣押人质而被捕，一周后死亡。辛贝特：“相关官员正在调查死亡情况”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-arrested-a-senior-doctor-in-gaza-six-days-later-he-died-in-a-shin-bet-facility/00000190-27eb-d14b-a999-27eb9aea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列疲惫不堪的军队需要休息，但内塔尼亚胡正在迫使以色列国防军继续在加沙作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-exhausted-troops-need-a-respite-but-netanyahu-is-forcing-the-idf-to-fight-on/00000190-27d3-d2de-af9e-67f30d870000</link><description>以色列军方高层希望结束拉法行动，让部队休息一下，并为北部可能出现的升级做好准备，但总理态度依然强硬，双方很可能迟早发生冲突 ■ 拜登特使正在穿梭耶路撒冷和贝鲁特之间的冲突，以防止北部边境局势升级，但他的大部分说服工作将针对以色列官员</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-exhausted-troops-need-a-respite-but-netanyahu-is-forcing-the-idf-to-fight-on/00000190-27d3-d2de-af9e-67f30d870000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡猛烈抨击拜登推迟武器装备；布林肯：美国出于“担忧”审查向以色列运送的一枚炸弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article-live/report-two-key-democrats-in-u-s-congress-approve-major-arms-sale-to-israel/00000190-2928-d5f5-a5d6-e9ea3c9c0000</link><description>真主党播放无人机镜头，据称显示监视以色列海法港 ■ 黎巴嫩发射火箭后，以色列北部起火 ■ 法国法院取消对以色列公司的禁令，允许他们参加军火博览会 ■ 美国希望避免黎巴嫩沿线“更大规模的战争” -以色列边境特使霍赫斯坦表示 ■ 联合国人权事务高级专员对加沙战争各方无视人权的行为感到“震惊” ■ 以色列警察镇压反政府抗议活动，八人被捕，数人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article-live/report-two-key-democrats-in-u-s-congress-approve-major-arms-sale-to-israel/00000190-2928-d5f5-a5d6-e9ea3c9c0000</guid></