w-west-bank-settlements-sanctions-against-palestinian-authority/00000190-27bf-d14b-a999-27ffd8830000</link><description>安全内阁考虑对拉马拉在国际论坛上针对以色列的法律运动采取惩罚措施。斯莫特里奇推动定居点建设，以回应其他国家承认巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-discusses-new-west-bank-settlements-sanctions-against-palestinian-authority/00000190-27bf-d14b-a999-27ffd8830000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级特使：以色列与真主党的战争可能导致伊朗大规模袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/top-u-s-envoy-israeli-war-with-hezbollah-could-lead-to-wide-scale-iranian-attack/00000190-27c4-d66b-abfd-7fe6eb620000</link><description>阿莫斯·霍赫斯坦周一在与包括总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长在内的一系列以色列官员会面时发出了警告</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/top-u-s-envoy-israeli-war-with-hezbollah-could-lead-to-wide-scale-iranian-attack/00000190-27c4-d66b-abfd-7fe6eb620000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战事中，内塔尼亚胡与以色列将军之间的激烈战争愈演愈烈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-fighting-in-gaza-the-war-between-netanyahu-and-israels-generals-is-intensifying/00000190-279c-d5f5-a5d6-effe367b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和以色列国防军之间在加沙战争问题上的分歧变得如此严重，以至于内塔尼亚胡阵营现在指责军队将军们采用了法西斯政党所青睐的经典“背后捅刀子”阴谋论。但这是一种冒险的策略，甚至是危险的策略</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-fighting-in-gaza-the-war-between-netanyahu-and-israels-generals-is-intensifying/00000190-279c-d5f5-a5d6-effe367b0000</guid></item><item><title>数万名以色列人发起一周反对政府的抗议活动：“我们不会放弃”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/tens-of-thousands-of-israelis-launch-week-of-protests-against-government-wont-give-up/00000190-275b-d340-a1f8-2f5fc20c0000</link><description>抗议者呼吁举行选举、加沙停火和释放人质协议，并谴责哈雷迪征兵豁免</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/tens-of-thousands-of-israelis-launch-week-of-protests-against-government-wont-give-up/00000190-275b-d340-a1f8-2f5fc20c0000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔警察如何威胁以色列的新闻自由</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-17/ty-article/.highlight/how-ben-gvirs-police-threaten-press-freedom-in-israel/00000190-26ca-d66b-abfd-7fee84ea0000</link><description>在报道抗议活动时，我会把记者证挂在脖子上，希望骑警不会因为骑车碾压记者而感到头疼。但随着政府削弱以色列的新闻自由，我开始怀疑它是否很快会让我成为目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:09:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-17/ty-article/.highlight/how-ben-gvirs-police-threaten-press-freedom-in-israel/00000190-26ca-d66b-abfd-7fee84ea0000</guid></item></channel></rss>